Michael Simpson, PA-C

Michael Simpson graduated from Eastern Virginia Medical School in Norfolk, VA in 2013. He also holds a Bachelors Degree in Respiratory Therapy and a Masters Degree in Cardiopulmonary Physiology, both from Salisbury University. He is married and has three children. He enjoys the beach, surfing, hunting and spending time with family.
